These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-1::.
3 different games are played: poker, monopoly, go
1. the person playing go is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person playing go##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |  2   |   3    |
| Game   | poker | monopoly | go |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-2::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: techno, funk, electronic
1. the fan of funk is on the far left or far right##3
2. the fan of electronic is in the middle##1
3. the fan of electronic is on the right of the fan of techno##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |   2   |   3   |
| Music-Genre   | techno | electronic | funk |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-3::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: soccer, skateboarding, water-polo
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |  2   |  3   |
| Sport   | skateboarding | soccer | water-polo |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-4::.
