.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-6::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: swimming, lacrosse, badminton
1. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left or right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##3
2. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3       |
| Sport   | swimming | lacrosse | badminton |

