.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-7::.
3 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, rat, hamster
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |       2       |  3  |
| Pet   | guinea-pig | rat | hamster |

