.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-13::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, game, alhambra
1. the game-smoker is on the left or right of the alhambra-smoker##3
2. the alhambra-smoker is between the game-smoker and the havana-smoker##2
3. the game-smoker is on the left of the alhambra-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |     3     |
| Cigar   | game | alhambra | havana |

